{"tid":2168126,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"外資財團買入新創建巴士業務","createTime":"2020-08-21T13:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T11:51:31.000Z","uid":323643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65a77aab7b5dcd1f6b5b2461c9b71243e05f98c7","tid":2168126,"uid":323643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"新巴及城巴母公司新創建集團有限公司在星期五向公眾發新聞稿表示國際財團收購新世界第一巴士服務有限公司及城巴有限公司的全部權益，收購價為32億港元。<br />\n<br />\n今次收購新創建集團有限公司旗下的新巴及城巴是一個國際投資財團，財團由Temple Water Bravo Holding Limited  牽頭，亦聯同營運夥伴Ascendal Group Limited 及投資夥伴漢思能源有限公司一起收購新巴及城巴的全部權益。<br />\n<br />\n今次收購新巴及城巴的國際投資財團TempleWater Bravo 是一間私募股權投資公司，由Investec Bank （天達銀行）與張堃先生合資作成立。天達銀行是一間國際專業銀行和資產管理集團，提供一系列金融產品和客戶服務，銀行亦都是倫敦證券交易所和約翰內斯堡證券交易所上市公司。張堃則曾經在周大福匯豐銀行及德意志銀行等企業在香港投資銀行部門工作。<br />\n<br />\n根據新聞稿表示交易完成後新巴及城巴的董事會將會有所變動，新創建集團行政總裁馬紹祥及新巴及城巴其他管理層成員將會留任董事會。<br />\n<br />\nAscendal Group Limted 則負責為公共交通制定及執行方案，公司創辦人及主席在全球主要城市包括倫敦、新加坡及悉尼等都有豐富的交通變革經驗。<br />\n<br />\nTemple Water Bravo 表示將會盡最大努力確保業務運作如常，完成收購後營運模式、員工薪酬、待遇、雇傭條款及福利亦都會保持不變。作為公司投資夥伴的漢思能源執行董事亦都表示很高興有今次的投資合作機會希望可以讓公司參與香港公共服務事業。<br />\n<br />\n閱讀更多：<br />\n【制裁伊朗】美國指控伊朗違反核協議承諾 要求聯合國恢復制裁伊朗 但遭其他成員國反對<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/583998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F583998&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=bbad9d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/583998</a><br />\n【中國外交策略】中國將向具有戰略意義的國家優先供應疫苗，以鞏固中國於全球的外交地位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/580899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F580899&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=449e451c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/580899</a><br />\n▶️滴水穿石，改變始於一念之間。訂閱FI Prime獨家內容：<a href=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=87c33551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/</a><br />\n▶️追蹤Youtube盡覽精華片段：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAcOhBfeztkBOBICFAj1YJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCAcOhBfeztkBOBICFAj1YJA&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=221d2a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAcOhBfeztkBOBICFAj1YJA</a><br />\n▶️追蹤 Instagram 以獲取最新資訊：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fortuneinsight/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffortuneinsight%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=59b02053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/fortuneinsight/?hl=zh-hk</a><br />\n#FortuneInsight #新巴及城巴 #Temple Water Bravo #收購 #FI<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n若有任何財金市場、初創、商業的新聞稿或廣告合作，歡迎電郵至：info@fortuneinsight.com<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/127745917936616/posts/624508751593661/?extid=zsDT0Dam7SqpVv7L&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F127745917936616%2Fposts%2F624508751593661%2F%3Fextid%3DzsDT0Dam7SqpVv7L%26d%3Dn&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=76b68c2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/127745917936616/posts/624508751593661/?extid=zsDT0Dam7SqpVv7L&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"f2c3a04c9464492bf36f70290e397e02cd42d13a","tid":2168126,"uid":323643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fc80d92dc64ef5e1f9075088a9e2c6d73f4af60","tid":2168126,"uid":132859,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"即係中資？"},{"pid":"ff9df9f8f4d3027c0f693e35931b80d5dc88c249","tid":2168126,"uid":224075,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedB